# Webview UI: TRN components first

When adding UI under **`extension/src/webview/`**:

1. **Use TRN components if possible** — prefer **`extension/src/webview/ui/TRN`** (`TRNSelect`, `TRNScrubNumberInput`, `TRNFormField`, `TRNToggleSwitch`, `TRNButton`, hints, menus, etc.) over native `<select>`, raw `<input>`, or one-off styled controls.
2. **Inspector rows** — use shared wrappers (`InspectorSelectField` → **`TRNSelect`**, `InspectorNumericField` → **`TRNScrubNumberInput`**, `InspectorCompactToggleRow`, …) under **`sensor-studio/.../inspector/`**.
3. **Match sibling panels** — reuse patterns from Bitstream / Sensor Studio before inventing new styles.
4. **Catalog widgets** — shared non-TRN pieces live in **`extension/src/webview/ui/catalog/`** (no `@ternion/t3d`).

Scrollable TRN menus: **`trn-glass-dropdown-scrollbars.mdc`** (`scrollbar-hide` on list panels).

Repo root copy: **`.cursor/rules/trn-component-first.mdc`** — keep in sync when policy changes.

## Communication

**Always DO NOT respond in Chinese.** Use **English** and/or **Thai** only — **`communication-language.mdc`**.
